videos.headline: Williams jukes two defenders for a UCF TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel lobs one to Marlon Williams, who does the rest on a 54-yard touchdown for UCF.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams jukes two defenders for a UCF TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams gets his feet down for UCF TD before the half
videos.description: Marlon Williams records his second touchdown of the half with a nice catch in the corner of the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams gets his feet down for UCF TD before the half) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gabriel and Williams have third TD connection of game
videos.description: UCF easily converts on 4th-and-12 as Dillon Gabriel goes deep to Marlon Williams for their third touchdown connection of the game.
